//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
// Waits until the specified simulation time. The simulation time is the number of
// seconds that have elapsed since the world started.
//
// # Params:
//   sim_time:
//     Simulation time in seconds of when to wake up.
//
// # Examples:
//   actor.
//     [
//     _move_to_node('Waypoint5')
//     _wait_until(25)  // Wait until 25 seconds since world start
//     _move_to_node('Waypoint6')
//     ]
//
// # Notes:
//   This does not stop the object from running other coroutines, it just holds off
//   calling the next routine(s) following the wait.
//
// # See:       _wait() 
// # Author(s): Conan Reis
//---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

(Real sim_time)

